title: Cryptoken Media Marketing Proposal #2
body:
Cryptoken Media has created a 7-week marketing and advertising strategic plan, which has the potential to be extended over the long run. The main goal of the planned campaign is twofold: to promote SportX.Bet and SX Network, if approved our core team will work with cryptoken to create content and market materials.

Full proposal details:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1i9NY9e8nx03Kj9amdsIc7NrIhxXWVvi6R06gLdsPJF8/edit#gid=777730279

About Cryptoken Media
Cryptoken Media is a boutique full-service agency, specialized in the delivery of global and local marketing campaigns to clients that operate only in the crypto and blockchain industry. Cryptoken Media has been on the market for nearly 4 years and has a very diversified and prominent portfolio of over 40+ companies, including Binance, Liquid, EtoroX, Huobi, 1Xbit, and numerous ICO/IEO/IDO/STO projects. The company provides full 360-degree solutions and is connected with 10,000+ businesses worldwide, enabling the delivery of even the most complex and highest in scale campaigns.

Results of first proposal are shared in discord! Ask team if you cannot find it.

Funding Request:
$29,470

$26,000 of marketing spend
$3,470 in fees to Cryptoken
